<P><HI>The Spirit of Independence:</HI> AN ORATION, DELIVERED BEFORE THE PROVIDENCE ASSOCIATION OF <HI>MECHANICS</HI> AND <HI>MANUFACTURERS,</HI> AT THEIR ANNUAL ELECTION, April 14, 1800.</P>
<P>BY TRISTAM BURGES, A. M.</P>
<P>PRINTED BY B. WHEELER, PROVIDENCE. 1800.</P>
</DIV1>
