<P>TO the A&s;&s;ociation at who&s;e Reque&s;t this Oration is publi&s;hed, it is mo&s;t re&s;pectfully in&s;cribed by</P>
<CLOSER><SIGNED>Their very humble Servant, TRISTAM BURGES.</SIGNED>
<DATELINE>Providence, <DATE>April 15th, 1800.</DATE></DATELINE></CLOSER>
